      "parameters": {
        "content": "🛒 E-commerce Order & Inventory Workflow\n\nMonitors new orders every 5 minutes, checks inventory \nlevels, notifies the warehouse via email and \nautomatically updates stock levels in Google Sheets.\n\nNodes:\n**Step 1**\n▶ Schedule Trigger — Checks for new orders every 5 mins\n\n**Step 2**\n📊 Google Sheets — Reads new orders from Orders Sheet\n\n**Step 3**\n⚙️ Code in JavaScript — Processes order details\n\n**Step 4**\n📊 Google Sheets1 — Reads current inventory levels\n\n**Step 5**\n⚙️ Code in JavaScript1 — Checks stock & detects low stock\n\n**Step 6**\n📧 Gmail — Sends warehouse notification draft\n\n**Step 7**\n⚙️ Code in JavaScript2 — Prepares inventory update data\n\n**Step 8**\n📊 Google Sheets2 — Updates stock levels in Inventory Sheet",
